channel.title: Live: European Championship Artistic Gymnastics
channel.desc: Matt Baker hosts coverage from the men's floor and pommel horse finals and women's vault and uneven bars finals at the European Championships in Leipzig, Germany. Great Britain's Jake Jarman won bronze in the men's floor event at the 2024 Paris Olympics and begins amongst the leading contenders in Germany. Olympic bronze medallist Beth Tweddle provides expert analysis.
